transcripts: This is the all in one dorm kit from Bed Bath & Beyond. This stylish kit includes bedding, towels, and storage. It comes in two sizes. The twin twin excel size kit is an 8 piece set which includes one comforter, one sham, flat sheet, one fitted sheet, one pillow case, two towels, and a storage organizer. The sheet set, the low case, and towels are 100% cotton. The full size kit is a 10 piece set which includes the same items but you get two shams and two 100$ pillow cases. All the pieces for either size kit come in this reusable storage organizer. The organizer features removable shelves and can hang on your closet for extra storage. The kit is available in four great patterns. Riley, Joanna, Chase, and Sebastian. The all in one dorm kit is available online or at a Bed Bath and Beyond near you.
